                            <comment id="13634234" author="apurtell" created="Wed, 17 Apr 2013 17:38:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ping &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=himanshu%40cloudera.com&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;himanshu@cloudera.com&quot;&gt;Himanshu Vashishtha&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13634240" author="v.himanshu" created="Wed, 17 Apr 2013 17:46:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, this is identical to 2611. Feng, can you try 0.94.5 while enabling &quot;multi&quot; property (have zk server versions &amp;gt;=3.4).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13634718" author="fenghh" created="Thu, 18 Apr 2013 01:10:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;OK, I&apos;m using hbase 0.94.3 and came up with this issue when reading code of replication rs failover. Very glad it&apos;s fixed already. Please Lars help close it as duplicated or fixed? Thanks&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
